text: Rotbusch is a locality in the municipality Schmallenberg in the district Hochsauerlandkreis in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. The hamlet has 8 inhabitantsSchmallenberg.de: Inhabitants and lies in the west of the municipality of Schmallenberg at a height of around 510 m. Rotbusch borders on the villages of Brenschede, Bracht, Hebbecke and Gleierbrück. ==References== Category:Villages in North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Schmallenberg
